  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Women with breast cancer and breast cancer survivors are often bothered by menopausal
      symptoms to a special degree. Treatment options for those symptoms are currently limited as
      hormone replacement therapy is often prohibited. Yoga has been shown to reduce menopausal
      symptoms as well as symptoms associated with breast cancer. Therefore, this study aims to
      investigate whether a 12-week yoga intervention can reduce menopausal symptoms in women with
      breast cancer and breast cancer survivors.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
